channel.title: Strange and weird
channel.description:
Yes, I maybe be not as advanced as some of you coders, but I do try. This is all before you flame with your comments or anything.
So here we go. I try to log into my server (ChiefScape Source), I've edited a couple of things and all of that, but yet when I log in, I get a unexpected log out after like 2 seconds of getting in. Does anyone know why?
Thanks.

When you’ve edited the source, what did you change?

If it runs fine then it would be because you’ve edited it.

I hope this helps.
